                    </div>
                    <span>This book has a huge variety of ceremonies that can easily be adapted to suit many belief systems.  I was surprised at how nicely everything was worded.  I found a lot of ceremonies that I could use and a few that I'll be able to use if the situation comes up.  It almost impossible to find good funeral ceremonies, but this book is full of them.  All the ceremonies are loving and uplifting.  Excellent book!  Something a lot of ministers have been waiting for!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Excellent Book for Ministers</div>
